//
// Identical surface change to fixture #2 (one new export added,
// nothing removed) but the developer has chosen to declare an
// explicit but empty `major_version_bump {}` catalog. An empty
// catalog is benign: it asserts "I've considered breaking changes
// and there are none." This is allowed and pinning it ensures the
// checker doesn't treat empty catalogs as suspicious.
//
// Expected: pass with zero diagnostics. The empty catalog is the
// honest declaration of "no removals, no renames, no breakage."

bismillah RegistryV2Bumped {
